孫"},{"pid":"ced34612e0b86dd713fcd977ba7bb1eb77bd645e","tid":199075,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb204a4135ca2b98d215e311ef259fc56d89821","tid":199075,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢會唔會想你咁樣先?<br />\n<br />\n開開心心就係最孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢唔會想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我無辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e50ccb4e6c59e48262baf28d05cca728ee5e8e43","tid":199075,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:03:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呀嫲走左三年我都未放低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真 點會放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93897d5d826dbb419b3ff9db3ad89acf9c3f38c","tid":199075,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:06:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呀爺香個陣我聽聽下歌聽到徐佳瑩都會係街喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時去探嫲嫲，聽嫲嫲講起，又或者見到啲舊相遺物，我都會搵藉口去一二邊喊<br />\n比多d時間自己囉，我都好幾個月先無咁易喊</blockquote><br />\n嫲嫲過左身之後 上老人院執翻佢啲野果陣 真係好心痛 喊到野都講唔到"},{"pid":"6bd43d728300361fffb80d07fc836e178b532585","tid":199075,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嫲係我15歲果年走左<br />\n佢最後果兩年。我青春期。唔識表達。每次番去探佢。都冇咩交流。其實佢內心係好掛住我 好想見多我一陣。<br />\n呢樣係我人生既遺憾之一<br />\n因為我醒覺果時<br />\n佢已經係病床。係最後果一段日子<br />\n最後仲走埋<br />\n<br />\n經過左佢離世之後。我對待另外三個老人家態度變左。陪佢地去醫院覆診。接出院入院。探病等等。我都親力親為。<br />\n我改變唔到grandma 果段日子。但仲在生既。我會好好對待。我自己亦好好成長。我要做令佢覺得驕傲既孫</blockquote><br />\n真係好好珍惜佢地三個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有時唔好怕醜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif